data.title: [FRAMEWORKS]
data.content: Economically Australia is very different to rest of the Global North. It's true when they say Australia is first world country with third world economy.  Majority of Australian businesses are still independent and owner operated. I love connecting with them, help them to tell their stories. Where possible, always buy or use local. This is  Mick from Belconnen, ACT.  #localsmatters #madeinaustralia #newselfwales
